Revitalize your new tab with the exhilarating Ferrari Live Wallpaper! This Chrome extension brings the iconic Ferrari flair right to your browsing experience.

The Ferrari Live Wallpaper extension showcases the stunning design and vibrant colors of this legendary sports car, creating an immersive backdrop for every new tab. Its sleek design not only enhances aesthetics but also offers essential tools for seamless navigation.

Quickly search the web using the Google search bar, access your favorite sites with customizable shortcuts, and stay organized with a clock-date display.

Key Features:

Live Wallpaper featuring the iconic Ferrari
Google Search Bar for easy browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for quick access to your top websites
Clock-Date display to keep you on track

Feel the speed and luxury of a Ferrari with every new tab! Visit Gameograf.com for more exciting themes to personalize your browsing.
